LanguageData.Miho_Elegans_Hediff.description: The mist flower organ, or the organ of elegans, is an organ that exists only in Miho's body, and it activates water-soluble mecanites and spreads them throughout the body. One of the reasons why it is called the elegans organ is that the tubes spread throughout the body are like the stem of the elegans flower. \n\n In order to maintain the Elegans Organ, you must periodically supply mecanite through helianto.
